@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About — Shane Khryss Bantilan</PageTitle>

<div class="page">
    <div class="page-header">
        <span class="page-eyebrow">About Me</span>
        <h2 class="page-title">Behind the<br /><em>Screen</em></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="about-grid">
        <!-- Left column -->
        <div>
            <div class="photo-stack">
                <div class="photo-deco"></div>
                <div class="photo-main">
                    <img src="profile.png" alt="Shane Khryss Bantilan"
                         onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'" />
                    <div class="photo-placeholder-inner" style="display:none">SKB</div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Right column -->
        <div class="about-body">
            <p>
                I am a 2nd-year Bachelor of Science in Information Technology student at
                Cebu Technological University – Daanbantayan Campus, currently
                serving as an SSG Multimedia Staff. In this role, I support basic
                layout design, photography, and occasional video editing.
            </p>
            <p>
                While I am still in the early stages of developing my skills, I am gaining practical
                experience through consistent exposure and hands-on practice. I am able to communicate
                effectively in English, Bisaya, and Tagalog, allowing me to collaborate
                smoothly within diverse teams.
            </p>
            <p>
                At this stage, I am focused on strengthening my foundation in programming, web
                development, and multimedia design. Although I have not yet built extensive projects,
                I am actively engaged in continuous learning and skill development.
            </p>
            <p>
                I am highly motivated to grow, adapt, and refine my capabilities, with the goal of
                becoming a competent and well-rounded IT professional capable of contributing to both
                technical and creative fields.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
